Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:08.97,0:00:12.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a soldier 而那也就是說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:12.21,0:00:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是被告也是法官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:15.41,0:00:21.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我同時站在火線的兩端
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:22.12,0:00:28.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繞過危險的轉角  追過生與死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.59,0:00:34.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我奔向前挑戰謊言的影子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.29,0:00:41.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無論編織出多少謊言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:41.10,0:00:48.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真相還是會照出光明的輪廓
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.01,0:00:50.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:50.68,0:00:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給那一天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:52.28,0:00:55.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當我們的痛苦都拋在腦後
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:55.55,0:00:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,站起來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:57.18,0:00:58.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.79,0:01:02.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是士兵不是站著就是死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:02.22,0:01:03.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,留著你的眼淚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:03.82,0:01:05.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,占好你的位置
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:05.36,0:01:08.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,把它們留給審判之日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:08.66,0:01:10.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快速而且自由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:10.30,0:01:11.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟著我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:11.93,0:01:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犧牲的時候到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:16.84,0:01:20.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們只能奮起或是倒地
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:20.91,0:01:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,攻殼機動隊 S.A.C 2nd GIG
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:35.39,0:01:36.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽我說！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:36.19,0:01:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無名的人們啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:38.09,0:01:40.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是個別的11人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:40.46,0:01:42.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,集合維持獨立的個體
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:42.36,0:01:45.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不斷改革世界的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:45.63,0:01:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個國家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.67,0:01:50.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作為系統的壽命已經瀕臨終結
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:51.14,0:01:53.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難民的自殺炸彈恐怖行為
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.47,0:01:54.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對政治的不信任
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:55.01,0:01:57.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,來自各國的摩擦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:57.58,0:01:59.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,包圍這個國家的情勢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:59.98,0:02:02.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,化為集合體的個人將拯救之
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.15,0:02:03.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,覺醒吧！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:03.98,0:02:05.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,無名的人們啊！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:06.15,0:02:08.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後成為系統的一部分
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:09.56,0:02:13.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,＃13  臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.19,0:02:17.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—喂!聲音有放進7點新聞嗎?\N—將難民的愚行視為宣戰佈告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:18.00,0:02:19.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—有放進去?\N—引導他們邁向解放
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.17,0:02:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—好 我們這邊來拍影像\N—我們堅決完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.83,0:02:23.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—小杉 你看那個\N—身為先驅應有的奉獻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.77,0:02:28.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,然後今天將執行最後的行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.18,0:02:37.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,繼承我們的意志！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.72,0:02:39.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—等一下\N—毋需多言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.19,0:02:44.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,頭...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:44.19,0:02:46.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他們用刀砍下了彼此的頭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:46.93,0:02:47.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一個接一個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.89,0:02:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,互相砍著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.30,0:02:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是難以置信的景象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:51.80,0:02:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,出現在屋頂的男子們
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.47,0:02:54.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—停\N—似乎拿刀互砍而死
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:54.73,0:02:59.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這就是昨天下午七點突然出現在國營電視臺上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.24,0:03:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,個別的11人的影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:01.77,0:03:05.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,心想他們總算現身了\N怎麼突然鬧自殺啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.48,0:03:10.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,讓人想起從合田的虛擬人格身上做人物側寫所得的結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.52,0:03:15.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,創造引發STAND ALONE COMPLEX現象的媒介者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:15.32,0:03:19.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“英雄因其死亡而誕生”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:19.79,0:03:25.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,與Patrick Sylvestre評論古巴革命的話一致的行動啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:25.80,0:03:31.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且還很細心地捏造“個別的11人”這個幻象
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:31.57,0:03:35.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巧妙掩飾這是病毒引起的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:35.44,0:03:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,除了我去見的那個記者之外
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:38.38,0:03:43.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全國應該還有很多人莫名其妙企圖自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:43.58,0:03:46.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也就是說我也很危險啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:47.02,0:03:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以確定程式
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.36,0:03:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早就設定好讓感染病毒的人最後去自殺
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:57.10,0:04:01.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難民已經用自爆的手段展開行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.50,0:04:06.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道這次自殺報導會出現多少模仿者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.44,0:04:09.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過這次應該會讓大多數不自覺的一般市民
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:09.21,0:04:15.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,深深瞭解到這個國家存在難民問題這個火藥庫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:16.05,0:04:19.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓感染病毒的病患再度出現症狀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:19.29,0:04:20.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們需要疫苗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.15,0:04:25.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,合田的計畫恐怕也不過是第一階段終了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:25.63,0:04:29.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然很擔心難民和模仿者的反應
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:29.30,0:04:33.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過人數居於劣勢的9課已經無法應付了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.60,0:04:37.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此我們要集中以內廳為目標
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:41.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了這個目的還是有必要抓住這個男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.28,0:04:43.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.34,0:04:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是這傢伙到底是怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:45.78,0:04:48.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼就他一個沒有自殺?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:48.31,0:04:51.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要正確找出理由
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.08,0:04:54.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不解析他本人的電子腦是不可能的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.92,0:04:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們鑒識人員之間
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.72,0:05:01.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,將這種感染同一病毒卻做出完全不同行動的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.63,0:05:04.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,稱為“突發性異變體”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:04.16,0:05:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那麼 從這個異變體的影像上面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.73,0:05:09.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能夠看出什麼新的資訊嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.47,0:05:10.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.54,0:05:11.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,首先
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.54,0:05:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請各位看這個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.54,0:05:16.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在襲擊首相時的影像中我們也注意到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.94,0:05:19.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙說話時不動嘴巴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.81,0:05:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就是這裡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:20.61,0:05:21.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,消失吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.25,0:05:22.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們一直以為在這時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:23.05,0:05:28.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他應該是為了提升義體表現故意切斷神經網路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:28.82,0:05:31.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這次也看到同樣行動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:31.12,0:05:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因此似乎可以得出不同的結論
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:33.99,0:05:35.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,—等一下\N—毋需多言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕這傢伙幾乎沒有使用
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:42.44,0:05:47.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,形成表情肌肉神經網路的微機械
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.01,0:05:49.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這表示他不動嘴巴?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.04,0:05:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 並非不動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.28,0:05:54.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而是幾乎不讓嘴巴動
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:54.61,0:05:57.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這能成為追蹤那傢伙的線索嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:57.55,0:05:58.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要急
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.88,0:06:00.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再來請看這傢伙的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:02.92,0:06:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他有一張很帥的臉 對不對？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:05.46,0:06:07.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這種事無關緊要吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.86,0:06:09.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們真是急性子啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:09.86,0:06:10.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之聽我說
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.06,0:06:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想說的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:12.67,0:06:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,排除表情肌肉的使用\N為什麼還能有這麼像人類的臉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:20.04,0:06:23.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,請技術高明的造顏作家做的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.71,0:06:25.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不愧是少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:25.78,0:06:30.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙的臉多半是超一流造顏作家的作品
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:31.15,0:06:32.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根據我的判斷
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.49,0:06:35.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,作者並非身邊大企業環繞的藝術家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.89,0:06:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這麼一來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.82,0:06:37.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有那種技術的作家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.79,0:06:40.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在國內只有兩名
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.20,0:06:49.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒想到造顏作家這麼珍貴啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.44,0:06:54.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原本就有人說日本人雖然手巧卻不擅長寫實的造型
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:54.67,0:06:56.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算會做既有的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:56.18,0:06:59.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 擁有感性能創造出獨一無二臉龐的藝術家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.55,0:07:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,的確是不多
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:00.81,0:07:01.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.42,0:07:05.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.93,0:07:14.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是9課的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.16,0:07:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發生什麼事了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:14.99,0:07:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的 好像是殺人案件的樣子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:19.20,0:07:22.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少校 剛到就碰到怪事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:22.67,0:07:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:23.57,0:07:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,調查對象有可能被滅口了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:25.87,0:07:27.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被搶先一步嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:27.57,0:07:28.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,還不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.71,0:07:31.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 縣警因為殺人案件封鎖了工作室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:31.58,0:07:33.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我派帕茲與齋藤過去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.35,0:07:35.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要讓現場被縣警弄亂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:35.51,0:07:36.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,恐怕已經來不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:38.92,0:07:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我們是9課
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.69,0:07:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以請你們所有人離開這裡嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.89,0:07:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,9課為什麼要出面干涉普通的殺人案?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:48.73,0:07:50.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被害人是造顏作家嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.83,0:07:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:52.03,0:07:55.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,實際上他是我們某追查中案件的重要關係人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:55.50,0:07:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是遺憾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:57.20,0:07:59.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 這件案子馬上就會解決
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.94,0:08:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抓到犯人之後會給你們情報
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:02.81,0:08:04.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以請乖乖回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:04.18,0:08:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說馬上就會解決是什麼意思?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:06.01,0:08:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.15,0:08:09.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,即使不是鑒識人員也馬上看得出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:09.98,0:08:11.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有沒有可能采到指紋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.42,0:08:14.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且嫌犯跟被害人認識
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.29,0:08:17.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到犯案之前還在一起喝酒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.92,0:08:19.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再加上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:20.16,0:08:24.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那裏的監視攝影機也清晰地拍下犯人的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.76,0:08:27.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我沒必要再進一步說明了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.63,0:08:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那給我們看看那個影像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:29.64,0:08:30.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.80,0:08:31.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你說什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:31.87,0:08:35.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也可以強制剝奪你的指揮權喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.14,0:08:37.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不會屈服在這種壓力下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.68,0:08:39.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這是我們的案子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.78,0:08:41.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂 巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:43.78,0:08:45.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看來不太平靜呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:53.53,0:08:54.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那張臉...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:58.60,0:08:59.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是誰?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.44,0:09:12.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,確實毫無疑問是帕茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:12.31,0:09:14.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,證物上的指紋怎麼樣了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:14.95,0:09:16.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,據說是一致的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.55,0:09:19.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,酒杯上的唇紋也一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.12,0:09:23.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,費盡功夫才阻止那批叫囂著要逮捕帕茲的縣警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:24.56,0:09:27.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,縣警那些人大概也能理解到
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.43,0:09:30.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這個影像無法當作決定性證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:30.16,0:09:33.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 連指紋和唇紋都一致事情可就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.37,0:09:34.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就算是這兩個證據
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:35.00,0:09:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不也都能偽造嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.00,0:09:41.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,連記錄在義體上的DNA資料都偷的到的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:41.21,0:09:43.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,假設犯人是那個義體混蛋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:43.94,0:09:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能發生這種事嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.38,0:09:47.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那恐怕很難想像
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:47.15,0:09:50.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或許只是恰巧跟某個別的案件撞在一起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.28,0:09:52.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕茲 有沒有想到什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:53.82,0:09:55.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,目前沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:55.52,0:09:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.39,0:09:58.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石川與波瑪從回收的資料上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.99,0:10:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,清查有沒有那個義體男子的記錄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:01.43,0:10:03.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴特、齋藤、德古沙跟縣警合作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:04.03,0:10:06.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追查造顏作家的命案
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.07,0:10:09.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕茲在嫌疑未洗清之前要注意自己的言行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:09.80,0:10:13.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想到跟案件有關的情報全部都要向我報告
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:13.47,0:10:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該有什麼理由才對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:16.68,0:10:17.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.15,0:10:27.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,到底怎麼回事?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:27.59,0:10:30.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該有想到什麼事情吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.29,0:10:32.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 沒有
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.73,0:10:35.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不方便跟少校說 找我也可以
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:35.59,0:10:37.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想起什麼事情的話就說出來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.66,0:10:39.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:49.38,0:10:51.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,成對的Death Mask\N（從死者臉上拓下的面模）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.74,0:10:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,老闆娘的新興趣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:56.02,0:10:57.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,歡迎光臨
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.02,0:11:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,給我跟他一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:04.09,0:11:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有何貴幹?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.62,0:11:07.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然想跟蹤你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:07.33,0:11:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過似乎馬上就會被發現
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.80,0:11:16.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其實我並不認為你是犯人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.70,0:11:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在這個城市當中\N連臉都義體化的傢伙並不稀奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.27,0:11:24.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是那不只是同一張臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.38,0:11:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,根本就跟你一模一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:27.75,0:11:32.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我從那段影像上面感覺到某種對你的執著
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:33.59,0:11:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,犯人絕對跟你有關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:36.32,0:11:38.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以讓我跟蹤你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:38.62,0:11:40.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今晚就是來打聲招呼的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.39,0:11:41.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隨便你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.77,0:11:49.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第一次看到呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:50.17,0:11:52.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你竟然會帶著男性同伴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.94,0:11:54.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大部分都是一個人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.04,0:11:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,或者永遠是不同的女性
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:57.91,0:11:59.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不認識的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:59.81,0:12:01.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:02.11,0:12:03.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,興趣變了嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:04.48,0:12:05.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是說那個？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.29,0:12:12.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,最近認識了一位元很棒的造顏作家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:12.89,0:12:14.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,造顏作家?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.33,0:12:18.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然請他替我做了新的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.83,0:12:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 在試戴他做的臉時
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:21.67,0:12:23.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我發現一件事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.74,0:12:27.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那就是靈魂有沒有可能不在腦殼裡面 而是在皮膚上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:27.84,0:12:32.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,尤其是寄宿在臉上所刻畫的皺紋當中呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:33.58,0:12:36.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽說那位造顏作家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.12,0:12:41.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一直替在戰場上負傷的士兵做新的臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:41.59,0:12:42.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:42.96,0:12:44.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他會發現臉上傷痕的深度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:44.79,0:12:49.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟那位士兵心中傷痕的深度是一樣的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.69,0:13:16.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼嘛 原來是你啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:22.93,0:13:23.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幹什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:26.00,0:13:26.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道說...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.40,0:13:33.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不就是這傢伙嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:34.84,0:13:36.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少校 找到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:37.34,0:13:38.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他名叫久世英雄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:39.58,0:13:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,全身都義體化了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:41.55,0:13:43.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從記錄上的規格來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.75,0:13:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是PKF型號的義體不會錯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:47.09,0:13:50.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,臉的訂單也如同鑒識官推理的那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.42,0:13:53.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,幾乎沒有安裝神經網路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:53.46,0:13:58.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是純粹靠造顏作家的技術\N表現出表情和皺褶的東西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.93,0:14:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,當然是獨一無二的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:00.70,0:14:03.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,材料是安裝有自我再生程式的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:03.80,0:14:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,納米碳分子以及人工生化皮膚的混合物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:07.61,0:14:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,原來如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.01,0:14:11.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然不知道有沒有直接關聯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:11.54,0:14:13.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過被殺害的造顏作家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.48,0:14:17.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,長年自願只替退伍軍人做臉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:18.55,0:14:21.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這傢伙多半是聽到這個傳言
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.65,0:14:23.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,才來找他做自己的臉吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.26,0:14:25.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,久世英雄嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.99,0:14:29.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,既然當時的記錄已經銷毀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:29.46,0:14:31.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只有直接去調查他的行蹤了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.03,0:14:32.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,石川
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:32.87,0:14:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做好飛去半島的準備工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:35.20,0:14:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這對老年人的身體不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.17,0:14:40.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是在那邊你最吃得開啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.64,0:14:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他跟這次的造顏作家命案沒有關聯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.41,0:14:45.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,應該是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.21,0:14:50.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 犯人跟帕茲有某種關係?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.18,0:14:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.62,0:14:54.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定出乎意料地跟女人有關
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.45,0:14:57.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少校 事情不好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.49,0:14:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:58.76,0:15:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,縣警的刑事被殺了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:02.66,0:15:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且被殺之前還跟帕茲見過面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.27,0:15:07.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕茲也在那裏?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.60,0:15:08.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:09.27,0:15:10.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.40,0:15:13.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很明顯這傢伙想要陷害帕茲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:13.94,0:15:15.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從掉在地上的彈殼來看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:15.61,0:15:19.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,用的是SEBURO M5的專用彈藥
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.38,0:15:21.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,做得太露骨了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:21.18,0:15:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,帕茲 事到如今\N還是沒想到什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.45,0:15:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不如說實在太多了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:27.12,0:15:28.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少校
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:28.32,0:15:30.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,被殺害的造顏作家的顧客資料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:30.92,0:15:33.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,從比較新的開始讓我看幾個
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:33.66,0:15:35.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,說不定會聯想到什麼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:35.66,0:15:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:36.50,0:15:37.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,波瑪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.20,0:15:49.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,少校 這個事件現在起請讓我一個人追查
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果造成什麼困擾的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:52.68,0:15:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以馬上把我幹掉沒關係
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.65,0:15:59.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這恐怕是非常私人的問題
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:00.69,0:16:02.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了 隨你高興怎麼做吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.86,0:16:04.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:10.43,0:16:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:11.50,0:16:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你要去哪裡？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:14.20,0:16:16.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你們是不是有什麼誤會啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:16.57,0:16:19.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,難道你們想說他是嫌疑犯嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.27,0:16:21.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,間接證據是這麼說的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.74,0:16:23.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 他是清白的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.71,0:16:25.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,總之要先查查看才知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:25.34,0:16:26.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有這個必要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.18,0:16:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有可能性的話 我們早就動手了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:36.89,0:16:37.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,巴特
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.46,0:16:42.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在你的外部記憶裡面輸入我現在要去的地方的位址
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.06,0:16:45.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果我沒有回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,麻煩你去那裏看看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.80,0:16:48.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.97,0:16:50.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你一個人沒問題嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.80,0:18:28.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真慢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.87,0:18:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你果然把我的事都忘了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.54,0:18:39.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過5年前 我們還住在這裡啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:40.28,0:18:43.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你從什麼時候開始佔據了那個女人的義體?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.55,0:18:45.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好像是3個月前吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:46.08,0:18:48.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在那裏偶然看到你的身影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:50.02,0:18:52.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你完全沒發現 對吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:52.46,0:18:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個女人的腦呢?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:55.06,0:18:56.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:56.46,0:18:59.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,現在應該在夢之島吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.43,0:19:02.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的指紋也是在那裏拿到的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:02.27,0:19:03.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:03.57,0:19:06.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為什麼想變成我?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:07.71,0:19:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我...
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:09.57,0:19:13.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,完全無法理解你在我面前消失的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.51,0:19:16.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,並沒有別的女人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:17.32,0:19:19.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也不是討厭我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:20.75,0:19:24.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因為你說不要問你的事我就照辦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:25.89,0:19:29.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可是你還是消失了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.86,0:19:33.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你第一次見到我的時候說的話
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.33,0:19:34.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你還記得嗎？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:35.50,0:19:38.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“我不跟同一個女人睡第二次”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:40.04,0:19:42.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,剛開始我還想這算什麼嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.97,0:19:45.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,第二次的時候我已經無法自拔了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:46.24,0:19:48.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這一點你應該也是一樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.75,0:19:51.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好殘忍的男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.82,0:19:54.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我瘋狂地恨著你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:55.45,0:20:00.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明如此 我還是不斷思考你消失的原因
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:01.06,0:20:02.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以才去做臉?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.86,0:20:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.93,0:20:05.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,發現了什麼嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:06.93,0:20:11.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對我愛的有多深
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:13.04,0:20:14.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你和我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.34,0:20:17.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看的簡直就是兩個世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.51,0:20:24.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,為了不讓我看到那個世界於是你選擇消失
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:24.52,0:20:25.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要自視過高
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:26.35,0:20:29.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 你就是這種人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.76,0:20:31.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是已經不重要了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:32.66,0:20:36.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我已經在身體裡面放進了你的靈魂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:37.70,0:20:41.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以已經不需要真正的你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.32,0:20:59.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果對我還有愛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:59.55,0:21:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就請你死在這裡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:03.42,0:21:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可以啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:05.29,0:21:08.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,如果被你所殺 正合我願
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:22.07,0:21:22.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,追！
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.11,0:21:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,瞭解
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:54.17,0:21:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,搞定了嗎?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:15.23,0:22:17.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,詳細情況就象剛剛報告的那樣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:17.60,0:22:19.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很有帕茲風格的故事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:19.66,0:22:20.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,算是吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:22.20,0:22:22.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:23.60,0:22:25.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他應該更早發現才對吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:26.54,0:22:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是嗎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:27.91,0:22:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想要殺他的女性說不定非常多喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:32.28,0:22:33.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的假的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:33.48,0:22:35.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,雖然我沒有確認過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:35.75,0:22:38.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不過 當初去招攬他的時候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:38.38,0:22:42.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,他也跟我說過“我不跟同一個女人睡第二次”
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:42.89,0:22:43.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什麼?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:44.76,0:22:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是敗給他了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:46.89,0:22:47.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,話說回來
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:47.93,0:22:51.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那個帕茲應該是真的吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:52.53,0:22:53.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大概吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:10.52,0:23:17.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找出我體內行星和星星的銀河
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:17.19,0:23:23.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽著它們每一個都唱著同樣寧靜的旋律
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.73,0:23:27.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在現實當中從來沒看過
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.73,0:23:30.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,這樣的美麗事物
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:31.04,0:23:35.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,沒有一點懷疑或恐懼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:35.51,0:23:39.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到一個聲音—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:39.78,0:23:42.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字—然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:42.25,0:23:46.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我審視自身—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.22,0:23:49.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我—時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:49.49,0:23:52.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:52.89,0:23:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去讓這一切成真的—它就在裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:57.90,0:24:02.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在軀殼裏的美麗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.10,0:24:06.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我聽到一個聲音—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.24,0:24:08.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,聽到一個聲音呼喚我的名字—然後現出光明
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:08.97,0:24:12.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我審視自身—醒來吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.94,0:24:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看到一道光隨時都圍繞著我—時間已經到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.11,0:24:19.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所有真相 所有我需要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:19.62,0:24:24.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,去讓這一切成真的—它就在裡面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就在這個軀殼裏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:32.50,0:24:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（攻殼車式的日常生活）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:43.78,0:24:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,（攻殼車式的日常生活）
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:56.35,0:24:57.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那傢伙看太多情報被感染了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:57.92,0:24:58.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快逃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:58.76,0:25:01.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,要是進入代理程式的射程內就麻煩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:05.43,0:25:07.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,離這麼遠應該沒問題了吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:07.77,0:25:08.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,對啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:25:09.13,0:25:09.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎麼了
